				<wikidot:authorName>Mortos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1705184</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>all traces of personality and ability to eat, sleep, see, vocalize and move any portion of the body other than the right arm have all been destroyed due to prolonged exposure to aberrant memes.</p> </blockquote> <p>Yeah the internet is a real bitch.</p> <p>+1 because the article itself is good, but except for a brief mention of a big bird, I don't see how this ties into your doomsday event.</p> 
				 	]]>
