					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5973571#post-3806580</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5973571/scp-3662#post-3806580</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 20 May 2018 13:09:18 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ribby97</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2299134</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's a neat idea, but&#8230;.</p> <p>I'm usually completely rubbish at working out complicated scips, but I /think/ I got what was happening here pretty early on in the interview, which meant that the newspaper article felt somewhat superfluous and heavy-handed.</p> <p>So I feel I have to no-vote, sorry :(</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">The&nbsp;comments&nbsp;make&nbsp;me&nbsp;think&nbsp;I've&nbsp;missed&nbsp;something</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">This&nbsp;is&nbsp;what&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;assuming&nbsp;happened</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Guy's daughter is dying, he puts her mind in a thing, then puts it in the body of a different girl, so her mind gets trapped in the thing.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5973571#post-3806233</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5973571/scp-3662#post-3806233</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 20 May 2018 04:18:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>LordStonefish</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2527320</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The clipping accurately captures the feel of a rural paper with very small readership from that time. But the masterpiece here is the combination of a complex technobabble heavy anomaly with a good story and just the right dash of doomsday and portention.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
