					<![CDATA[
						 <p><a href="http://scpexplained.wikidot.com/scp-3662">http://scpexplained.wikidot.com/scp-3662</a></p> <p>This took me a lengthy discussion in chat with Aers to understand, and I think a lot of people just won't get this. So I must continue my duty of Aers's designated explainer <sub><sup>(you know, if you didn't write such complicated shit i wouldn't need to be here :p)</sup></sub> by drafting the SCP explained article above.</p> <p>I still think I might of gotten something backwards though, the diagram isn't quite matching up but I honestly don't know what to change at this point.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-692588-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-692588-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. I mean I could probably figure it out but at this point fuck it, the additional context part is what matters anyway.</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
